lucky is a 2012 kannada romantic film starring yash and ramya in the lead roles . the film is directed by dr. suri , a dentist by profession , who makes his debut in film direction . arjun janya is the music director of the film . actress turned producer , radhika kumaraswamy has produced the venture under &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; enterprises along with the assistance of h. d. kumaraswamy and v raghavendra bunty . the film released across karnataka cinema halls on 24 february 2012 .